怀疑态度</p>\n<h2>微软的影响</h2>\n<p>最近受到微软的影响较大，ChatGPT 比 Bard 更好用，Bing AI 也不错</p>\n<h2>日常使用 Office</h2>\n<p>日常使用 office （包括 onenote ）比较多，这些都是微软家的</p>\n<h2>Chrome 的局限</h2>\n<p>Chrome 现已变得庞大，缺乏真正的开发和创新，这让我想起了多年前的 IE</p>\n<h2>Edge 的吸引力</h2>\n<p>Edge 的边栏和竖向标签栏功能对我极具吸引力，几乎每天都在诱惑我进行尝试</p>\n<p>鉴于这些理由，我准备做出转变。你们呢？面对这样的选择，你们会怎么决定？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1700964473, "replies": 138, "id": 995182}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9bf3/1c7f/15_large.png?m=1696388671", "name": "twitter", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9bf3/1c7f/15_normal.png?m=1696388671", "title": "Twitter", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/twitter", "topics": 426, "footer": "关于 Twitter 的使用和开发的讨论。", "header": "Find out what’s happening, right now, with the people and organizations you care about.", "title_alternative": "Twitter", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9bf3/1c7f/15_mini.png?m=1696388671", "stars": 769, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 15, "parent_node_name": "internet"}, "member": {"id": 601784, "username": "dw2693734d", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/dw2693734d", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "I LOVE CHINA🇨🇳", "bio": "I LOVE CHINA🇨🇳", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fbcf/03e0/601784_mini.png?m=1698980376", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fbcf/03e0/601784_normal.png?m=1698980376", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fbcf/03e0/601784_large.png?m=1698980376", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fbcf/03e0/601784_xlarge.png?m=1698980376", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fbcf/03e0/601784_xlarge.png?m=1698980376", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/fbcf/03e0/601784_xlarge.png?m=1698980376", "created": 1668437368, "last_modified": 1698980376}, "last_reply_by": "fyq", "last_touched": 1701003490, "title": "如何屏蔽推特的政治话题？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/995289", "created": 1700985306, "deleted": 0, "content": "我只想用推特看看新闻和马